{"tid":1137160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大控煙新規：要求煙盒統一使用「最醜」顏色","createTime":"2019-05-03T14:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T14:59:56.000Z","uid":228346,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"faacfd8cffa5bd9bade03318fcf5abfa8d9f7313","tid":1137160,"uid":228346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"為推動控煙，加拿大聯邦政府決定實施新規，要求所有煙草製品外包裝盒必須統一使用單一、標準的褐色，加拿大媒體報道說，這是一種被市場營銷業界形容為&quot;天下最醜&quot;的顏色。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOBtWjU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOBtWjU.png&h=251c399e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，包裝上還必須使用展現吸煙健康風險的圖片。只有允許的文本可以以標準字體、顏色、字號和位置在包裝上顯示，其它獨特和誘人的元素都必須被去除。另外，煙草製品外殼及煙草產品外形等也須採用統一的設計。比如，超細、超長的所謂&quot;時尚&quot;或&quot;新潮&quot;造型的香煙將不復存在。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，新規將於今年 11 月上旬開始對製造商實施，並於 2020 年 2 月初全面落實到零售層面。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大癌症協會稱贊政府的新規，稱其為&quot;世界上最好，最全面的&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大官方數據顯示，每年約有 4.5 萬名加拿大人死於與吸煙有關的疾病。根據加拿大官方的控煙戰略，加政府要在 2035 年將煙民數量降至全國總人口的 5%。而目前煙民在其總人口中所佔比例為 17%。<br />\n<br />\n來自於 2000 年英國醫學雜誌發佈的《1950 年以來英國的吸煙、戒煙和肺癌狀況》這篇長達 50 年的調查論文得出以下 4 條結論：<br />\n<br />\n1、吸煙是肺癌的主要死因之一，年齡越大，肺癌風險越大；<br />\n<br />\n2、即使吸煙者人到中年以上，戒煙也能夠極大的降低肺癌風險；<br />\n<br />\n3、在 30 歲之前戒煙能夠規避 90% 以上吸煙相關疾病的風險；<br />\n<br />\n4、截止 1990 年，英國的戒煙運動直接導致肺癌患病率下降一半。"},{"pid":"412cc7d14df19358d4427218f773f0275bed5327","tid":1137160,"uid":77473,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"用左十秒搵隻色係邊"},{"pid":"7743f782404dea181d66a1cfa82d00d7827a07ae","tid":1137160,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"歧視白化症可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1458e48f3c1ddecfb2695312b291afc826e80777","tid":1137160,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:14:56.000Z","msg":"淨係見到king size<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e18d9a77b4408b27b43b890813fd29eb364ff85","tid":1137160,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"最柒一定係澳洲屎啡加 arial 牌子名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fdb8cf15e5b3a8f3f303a7e135b655e4b2162d","tid":1137160,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"412cc7d14df19358d4427218f773f0275bed5327","tid":1137160,"uid":77473,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:12:56.000Z","msg":"用左十秒搵隻色係邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"圖都佔左8、9成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b973d5c212bb713f7301e6c519da3ab4728dce33","tid":1137160,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"271173b13bda3a2f52fe5a0150e994a78b4252ef","tid":1137160,"uid":77569,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fcdc5367d3c4a2465dc4d1a6022678f3ac5519b1","tid":1137160,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"冇用香港個d夠核突la<br />\n咪又係大把人周街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61371cd978110253493ecea44224b144d8a453f4","tid":1137160,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"煙撚有煙就夠架啦<br />\n包裝wfc照食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要做就直接賣空盒撚鳩佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c827afef04c85a98d516563420f05fe106b6a5e8","tid":1137160,"uid":1159,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"fcdc5367d3c4a2465dc4d1a6022678f3ac5519b1","tid":1137160,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"冇用香港個d夠核突la<br />\n咪又係大把人周街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/n